
1. References
 - https://docs.brew.sh/Homebrew-and-Python.html
 
2. Pre-requisites
 - homebrew
 
3. Steps
 - install python3
  + brew install python3
 - update pip setuptools wheel
  + pip3 install --upgrade pip setuptools wheel
 - check the installation is done successfully
  + python3 --version
  + pip3 --version
  